HEADWORD: Cow
<hw>Cow</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Cows</plw> (kouz);
old pl. <plw>Kine</plw> <pr>(k⟦imac⟧n)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[OE.
<ets>cu</ets>, <ets>cou</ets>, AS. <ets>c⟦umac⟧</ets>; akin to D.
<ets>koe</ets>, G. <ets>kuh</ets>, OHG. <ets>kuo</ets>, Icel.
